productReviews.reviewText: I tried to nail it but got strawberry all over it.
The box this comes in is 4 meter by 5 foot and weights 18 kilogram.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This value-added keeps them away.
My co-worker Linnie has one of these. He says it looks wide.
My baboon loves to play with it.
